Introduction

Lee Seo-jeong (이서정), better known as Sei (세이), is the lead vocalist and rapper of the girl group Weki Meki under Fantagio Entertainment. She first appeared in Astro's music video for the song "Confession".

In 2016, Sei became a contestant on Mnet's survival show Produce 101, representing her company LOUDers Entertainment. She was eliminated in episode 5 after ranking 85th place. She signed with Fantagio Music after leaving her previous firm after the performance.

She debuted as a member of Weki Meki on August 8, 2017 with their first mini album 'Weme'.
